data.description: Well cared for brick ranch with full basement on just over two acres outside of Chillicothe city limits. Home sits very near the VA hospital, Hopewell Culture National Park, and Adena Mansion and Gardens and is a couple of miles from  US 23.  Perfect location for commuting needs. Home has new windows, spouting and back deck just installed last year. All exterior paint, including the shutters, has been treated by rhino shield. Basement and living room offers gas fireplaces. Auditor shows this as a 3 bedroom, one f the rooms was converted to a breakfast nook off the kitchen. Could easily be turned back into a bedroom. Professional photos to come soon. Be sure to schedule a showing soon, this one won't last long!
